ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000Mtbez:ref

Hi @Netwrix Support<mailto:techsupport@netwrix.com>,

Follow the answers below:

- What is the impact of the issue on your business?
High impact, we have more than 30 computers with problem.

- Have you attempted any troubleshooting steps yet? If so, what have you tried?
Yes, I tried in my own computer. At first, I tried to uninstall and install again, but the computer continued without connection on the server, before I tried to exclude the computer on the server, uninstall and install again the agent in my machine and now the computer does not appear in the panel.

- When did this issue start?
We noticed this problem last week after apply a new license to extend our computers number.

- Can you please let me know the Server (if not already known) on which the issue is encountered?
In our own EPP server.

- On what platform is your Endpoint Protector hosted? (on-prem, AWS, GCP, Azure, Hosted by EPP on AWS)
On-premise.

- Since you have some, can you provide screenshots, logs, other artifacts, etc.
I have already added the screenshots on the ticket.

- Can you navigate to System Configuration -> System Licenses and provide a screenshot?
It's strange also because we have 215 computers with agent, but only 162 are using license.
[cid:image003.png@01DB9426.39021EF0]

- Do you know if you have Automatic License release configured?
Yes, 240 days.


Thanks!
